lead_paragraph: Kirk Cousins unloaded on a throw down the right sideline and watched as receiver DeSean Jackson and cornerback Josh Norman raced after the ball.

headline.print_headline: Jackson vs. Norman Is Must-Watch Matchup of Redskins Camp
